data.description: Home is priced below the appraised amount!  Bring all offers!  Take a look at this lovely home!  Corner lot!  4 bedroom, 2 full baths with a split and open floor plan. This wonderfully maintained home is located in one of Bartow's most desirable communities, Taylor Landing. In the family room there is LVP (luxury vinyl planking) flooring over laminate. The bedrooms are carpeted. The backyard is fenced with PVC fencing and perfect for pets and a growing family. Two car garage.  HOA is low.  The home is conveniently located less than a mile and features lots of restaurants, bakeries, stores and even our own brewery!  Easy to access the Polk Parkway, I-4, Lakeland, and Winter Haven. The Fort Fraser Trail is approx. 7 miles and is just down the road for your biking, jogging or for taking that evening walk. Please make an appointment to see this home!
